message.text:
TODAY 3/3 is "Hina-matsuri," which is a special day in Japan. Families with young girls display a set of dolls and pray for their health and happiness!
Look! Jeff-kichi is enjoying the Hina Arare－a traditional snack for this special day.
今日はひな祭り、じぇふ吉も、ひなあられをつまみ食い～
